
Boil the penne pasta in a pan.Add 1/2 teaspoon oil so that it doesnt get stick together.
chop all vegetables and saute in a pan till shallow pink.next step is to make a sauce.take 2 teaspoon of
corn flour and add butter and now add milk slowly and stir it to mske a sauce.after your sauce is reday sprinkle salt,chilli flakes and black
pepper and stir again...after few minutes add you boil pasta and mix it well.

your tasty pasta is ready.